A correction is in order.<br><br>
I stated in a previous post that Bao Dai had &quot;abdicated to Diem&quot;. My mistake. He previously had abdicated his throne to the Viet Minh in 1945.<br><br>
Instead, he gave up his position as Prime Minister to Diem in 1954.
